genes were categorized as proteinase genes, six genes were related to protein
quality control, and some genes encoded unknown/hypothetical proteins.
Similarly, the down-regulated genes in the R1&#x00394;<italic>dr1790</italic> mutant
included four genes that were related to secreted proteins. The effectiveness of
the microarray data was further confirmed by real-time quantitative RT-PCR
(<xref rid="t04" ref-type="table">Table 4</xref>). Notably, many molecular
